    ![codeLearn_swapCharacters](../images/../CodeLearn/img/codeLearn_swapCharacters.png)

    #### CASE
    | input     | output |
    | :-------- | -----: |
    | "ab","ba" |   true |
    | "ab","ab" | false |
    | "aaaaaaabc","aaaaaaacb" | true |
